    <title>MarkDown(.md)教程</title>
    <url>/2025/03/09/makedown-firset/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h2 id="什么是-Markdown？"><a href="#什么是-Markdown？" class="headerlink" title="什么是 Markdown？"></a>什么是 Markdown？</h2><ul>
<li>一种轻量级标记语言</li>
<li>通过纯文本编写结构化内容</li>
<li>易读易写，可转换为 HTML&#x2F;PDF 等格式</li>
<li>广泛用于文档、博客、GitHub 等平台</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id="基本语法"><a href="#基本语法" class="headerlink" title="基本语法"></a>基本语法</h2><h3 id="1-标题"><a href="#1-标题" class="headerlink" title="1. 标题"></a>1. 标题</h3><div class="code-container" data-rel="Markdown"><figure class="iseeu highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section"># 一级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">## 二级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">### 三级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">#### 四级标题</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
<details class="red" data-header-exclude><summary><i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right"></i>实例＆效果 </summary>
              <div class='content'>
              <p><strong>示例：</strong></p><div class="code-container" data-rel="Markdown"><figure class="iseeu highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section"># 欢迎使用 Markdown</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">## 这是一个二级标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">### 这是一个三级标题</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p><strong>效果：</strong></p><p class='h1' id="欢迎使用-Markdown"><a href="#欢迎使用-Markdown" class="headerlink" title="欢迎使用 Markdown"></a>欢迎使用 Markdown</h1><p class='h2' id="这是一个二级标题"><a href="#这是一个二级标题" class="headerlink" title="这是一个二级标题"></a>这是一个二级标题</h2><p class='h3' id="这是一个三级标题"><a href="#这是一个三级标题" class="headerlink" title="这是一个三级标题"></a>这是一个三级标题</h3>
              </div>
            </details>

<hr>
<h3 id="2-段落与换行"><a href="#2-段落与换行" class="headerlink" title="2. 段落与换行"></a>2. 段落与换行</h3><ul>
<li>段落：直接换行文字</li>
<li>强制换行：行尾添加两个空格<br>或在段落间空一行</li>
</ul>
<details class="red" data-header-exclude><summary><i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right"></i>实例＆效果 </summary>
              <div class='content'>
              <p><strong>示例：</strong></p><div class="code-container" data-rel="Markdown"><figure class="iseeu highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">这是第一段文字。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">这是第二段文字。  </span><br><span class="line">这是同一段内的换行。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p><strong>效果：</strong><br>这是第一段文字。</p><p>这是第二段文字。<br>这是同一段内的换行。</p>
              </div>
            </details>

<hr>
<h3 id="3-列表"><a href="#3-列表" class="headerlink" title="3. 列表"></a>3. 列表</h3><p><strong>无序列表</strong></p>
<div class="code-container" data-rel="Markdown"><figure class="iseeu highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> 项目1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> 项目2</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">  -</span> 子项目</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>

<p><strong>有序列表</strong></p>
<div class="code-container" data-rel="Markdown"><figure class="iseeu highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">1.</span> 第一项</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">2.</span> 第二项</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
<details class="red" data-header-exclude><summary><i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right"></i>实例＆效果 </summary>
              <div class='content'>
              <p><strong>示例：</strong></p><div class="code-container" data-rel="Markdown"><figure class="iseeu highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> 苹果</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> 香蕉</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">  -</span> 黄香蕉</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">  -</span> 绿香蕉</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">1.</span> 第一步</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">2.</span> 第二步</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p><strong>效果：</strong></p><ul><li>苹果</li><li>香蕉<ul><li>黄香蕉</li><li>绿香蕉</li></ul></li></ul><ol><li>第一步</li><li>第二步</li></ol>
              </div>
            </details>

<hr>
<h3 id="4-强调"><a href="#4-强调" class="headerlink" title="4. 强调"></a>4. 强调</h3><div class="code-container" data-rel="Markdown"><figure class="iseeu highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">*斜体*</span> 或 <span class="emphasis">_斜体_</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">**粗体**</span> 或 <span class="strong">__粗体__</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">**<span class="emphasis">*粗斜体*</span>**</span> 或 <span class="strong">__<span class="emphasis">_粗斜体_</span>__</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
<details class="red" data-header-exclude><summary><i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right"></i>实例＆效果 </summary>
              <div class='content'>
              <p><strong>示例：</strong></p><div class="code-container" data-rel="Markdown"><figure class="iseeu highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">这是 <span class="emphasis">*斜体*</span>，这是 <span class="strong">**粗体**</span>，这是 <span class="strong">**<span class="emphasis">*粗斜体*</span>**</span>。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p><strong>效果：</strong><br>这是 <em>斜体</em>，这是 <strong>粗体</strong>，这是 <em><strong>粗斜体</strong></em>。</p>
              </div>
            </details>

<hr>
<h3 id="5-链接与图片"><a href="#5-链接与图片" class="headerlink" title="5. 链接与图片"></a>5. 链接与图片</h3><div class="code-container" data-rel="Markdown"><figure class="iseeu highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[<span class="string">链接文字</span>](<span class="link">https://example.com</span>)</span><br><span class="line">![<span class="string">图片描述</span>](<span class="link">image.jpg</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
<details class="red" data-header-exclude><summary><i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right"></i>实例＆效果 </summary>
              <div class='content'>
              <p><strong>示例：</strong></p><div class="code-container" data-rel="Markdown"><figure class="iseeu highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">访问 [<span class="string">Google</span>](<span class="link">https://www.google.com</span>)。</span><br><span class="line">![<span class="string">Markdown Logo</span>](<span class="link">https://markdown-here.com/img/icon256.png</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p><strong>效果：</strong><br>访问 <a class="link"   href="https://www.google.com/" rel="external nofollow noreferrer" >Google<i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right ml-[0.2em] font-light align-text-top text-[0.7em] link-icon"></i></a>。<br><img  
                     lazyload
                     src="/images/loading.svg"
                     data-src="https://markdown-here.com/img/icon256.png"
                      alt="Markdown Logo"
                ></p>
              </div>
            </details>
<hr>
<h3 id="6-代码"><a href="#6-代码" class="headerlink" title="6. 代码"></a>6. 代码</h3><p><strong>行内代码</strong></p>
<div class="code-container" data-rel="Markdown"><figure class="iseeu highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">使用 <span class="code">`print(&quot;Hello&quot;)`</span> 语法</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
<p><strong>代码块</strong></p>
<pre>
<div class="code-container" data-rel="Python"><figure class="iseeu highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;Hello World&quot;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
</pre>

<details class="red" data-header-exclude><summary><i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right"></i>实例＆效果 </summary>
              <div class='content'>
              <p><strong>示例：</strong></p><div class="code-container" data-rel="Markdown"><figure class="iseeu highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">这是行内代码：<span class="code">`print(&quot;Hello&quot;)`</span>。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">这是代码块：</span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">```python</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">def hello():</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    print(&quot;Hello World&quot;)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><div class="code-container" data-rel="Plaintext"><figure class="iseeu highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">**效果：**</span><br><span class="line">这是行内代码：`print(&quot;Hello&quot;)`。</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">这是代码块：</span><br><span class="line">```python</span><br><span class="line">def hello():</span><br><span class="line">    print(&quot;Hello World&quot;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
              </div>
            </details>

<hr>
<h3 id="7-表格"><a href="#7-表格" class="headerlink" title="7. 表格"></a>7. 表格</h3><div class="code-container" data-rel="Markdown"><figure class="iseeu highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">| 左对齐 | 居中对齐 | 右对齐 |</span><br><span class="line">| :----- | :------: | -----: |</span><br><span class="line">| 内容1  |   内容2  |   内容3 |</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>

<details class="red" data-header-exclude><summary><i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right"></i>实例＆效果 </summary>
              <div class='content'>
              <p><strong>示例：</strong></p><div class="code-container" data-rel="Markdown"><figure class="iseeu highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">| 姓名   | 年龄 | 职业     |</span><br><span class="line">| :----- | :--: | --------: |</span><br><span class="line">| 张三   |  25  | 工程师   |</span><br><span class="line">| 李四   |  30  | 设计师   |</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p><strong>效果：</strong></p><table><thead><tr><th align="left">姓名</th><th align="center">年龄</th><th align="right">职业</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="left">张三</td><td align="center">25</td><td align="right">工程师</td></tr><tr><td align="left">李四</td><td align="center">30</td><td align="right">设计师</td></tr></tbody></table>
              </div>
            </details>

<hr>
<h3 id="8-分割线"><a href="#8-分割线" class="headerlink" title="8. 分割线"></a>8. 分割线</h3><div class="code-container" data-rel="Markdown"><figure class="iseeu highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">或</span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">**<span class="emphasis">*</span></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>

<details class="red" data-header-exclude><summary><i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right"></i>实例＆效果 </summary>
              <div class='content'>
              <p><strong>示例：</strong></p><div class="code-container" data-rel="Markdown"><figure class="iseeu highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section">这是第一部分。</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">---</span></span><br><span class="line">这是第二部分。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><p class='h2' id="效果：这是第一部分。"><a href="#效果：这是第一部分。" class="headerlink" title="效果：这是第一部分。"></a><strong>效果：</strong><br>这是第一部分。</h2><p>这是第二部分。</p>
              </div>
            </details>

<hr>
<h3 id="9-引用"><a href="#9-引用" class="headerlink" title="9. 引用"></a>9. 引用</h3><div class="code-container" data-rel="Markdown"><figure class="iseeu highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="quote">&gt; 引用内容</span></span><br><span class="line">&gt;&gt; 嵌套引用</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>
<details class="red" data-header-exclude><summary><i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right"></i>实例＆效果 </summary>
